<div id="main_content">
	<h2>UCF Economist: White House Suffers from 'Audacity of Scope'</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Christine Dellert
		
		<span class="date">Sept. 8, 2009</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1868/en_US/centsmain.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: FreeDigitalPhotos.net</p>
			
			<p>Sean Snaith says the administration should completely roll out its fiscal stimulus before tackling other challenges. </p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041037381429012136c33d7901fa1">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
			<div id="related">
